Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:11.96,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,太豐收呢 千千石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:15.88,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是欠收吧 百道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:19.97,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集了這麼的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.60,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,也能獲得不錯的咒力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.68,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的不是量而是質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:28.10,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,全是雜魚 太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:30.35,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:51.29,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:52.50,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,暗無
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.63,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道 千千石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:59.30,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們可知道有人在各地封堵龍黑點？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:02.72,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是被稱為雙星的兩位陰陽師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:04.01,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,雙星？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:09.18,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,據說會生下神子 並為禍野帶來終焉的陰陽師夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:14.19,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,他們使用一種疊加彼此的咒力 使其倍增的秘術「共鳴」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.99,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,以此來封堵龍黑點 是最強的2人組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:20.70,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:21.99,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:25.53,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的2人組是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:30.12,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,當然沒有人能勝過你們這對搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:34.33,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那對雙星好像即將經過這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.92,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 好像很有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:38.76,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不 根本不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:46.43,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的 目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.47,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是解放禍野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.94,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,封堵龍黑點的可恨陰陽師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:54.15,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的話能夠打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:56.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.32,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:01.70,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾跟陰陽師玩玩也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.36,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,至少可以幫千千石找點樂子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 百道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:10.75,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,去確認一下雙星有多少斤兩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:12.29,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.65,T-title 方正 - 黑,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,910)}雙星vs雙生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.60,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝真是個不可思議的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.02,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在禍野中遇到的她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.69,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,可以平安無事地穿行於瘴氣中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:08.66,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,跟普通孩子……不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:14.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是擁有驚人咒力的年幼陰陽師……我們也做了不少猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.75,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,萩……萩餅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:20.25,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,萩餅太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.42,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.60,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,萬魔調伏 急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.65,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 明明時間就是金錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這下就是第四次白跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.16,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,29小時38分的浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 損失慘重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.75,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 至少堵上了一個龍黑點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.62,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,也不算完全白跑一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.75,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,新先生 那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.05,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這是「魔法少女嘭嘭皮娜」的最新一期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.76,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是發售日呢 我剛才在便利商店買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:17.06,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼能把祓除汙穢的工作推給我們 自己卻去悠閒地購物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.85,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪裡悠閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:24.65,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這是嘭嘭皮娜脫離險境 得到新魔法道具的重要一卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.28,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我作為嘭嘭皮娜的信徒 是以全心全靈的虔誠去購買的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.70,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個宅男
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:36.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好像又有動作了 婆娑羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.41,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定是他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:39.66,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.08,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這就必須去確認一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:42.33,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.63,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.34,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.21,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊轉 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.22,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.18,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊轉 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.55,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好 這次一定……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.18,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:58.89,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊轉 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.81,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,咕 全輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.15,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝好強啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.52,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你太弱了……而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.11,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 那麼你來試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.41,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.16,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊轉 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.54,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.70,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊轉 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.12,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.67,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊轉 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.38,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,全部輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.88,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到對手的習慣跟模式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.93,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,就能提高猜拳的勝率
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:43.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,而頭往哪轉 可以透過觀察準備動作來預判
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:44.56,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你怎麼跟小孩一般見識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.15,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這是認真對決
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.40,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是遊戲而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.15,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,明明你是認真地輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.15,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.57,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,完全贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:59.03,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,別……別哭啊 小枝 下次一定能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.54,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:01.79,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:02.58,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.58,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.08,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,用同樣的要領 故意輸掉就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:10.84,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.92,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.43,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊轉 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.85,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.60,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝 你好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.89,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,天……才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.43,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆都太寵她了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.35,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？不好！不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:31.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:32.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,禍野？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.45,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？什麼時候進來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.12,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,汙穢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.04,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我要衝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.41,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好好抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.91,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們看看俺的真本事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.96,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.09,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是專業式神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.47,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時離開這個地方……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:05.89,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.94,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.73,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 採用了這麼粗魯的迎接方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:20.24,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到禍野 雙星之陰陽師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.16,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,婆娑羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,婆娑羅 居然有2位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.66,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見到你們呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.54,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 不過馬上又要分別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:32.75,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的咒力強大到能夠封堵龍黑點 我們非常想嚐嚐看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:36.80,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 你們倆是我們的主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.01,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不 最多只算前菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.05,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.14,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,前菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:41.80,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.10,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,前菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:45.97,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.18,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.31,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:50.69,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:53.36,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會這麼容易被你們吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,黃粉 保護小枝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.78,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝 這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.32,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,星裝顯符焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:12.00,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,重奏陰陽術式 災星！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.29,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,白凜斗牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:33.40,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.28,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:49.70,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,太無力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.58,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,無刀朧蓮華
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.21,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,反閇飛燕式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:07.05,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.97,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成這就是你們的全力？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.73,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你們是認真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:13.94,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:14.90,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,轆轤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:21.11,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,焰磊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:21.90,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,紅擲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:23.82,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.12,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,裂空 魔雙彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.34,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.00,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,完全防下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.80,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是共鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.55,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.55,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,別笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:52.85,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.81,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不呼喚對方的名字就無法協同戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:01.03,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不發信號就無法使用共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.78,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.86,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們根本不需要信號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:10.74,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是一起誕生 一起行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.12,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是2人一體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.46,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,即便不交流也能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.88,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,即便沒有信號也能感應到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.13,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,千千石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:21.34,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.21,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.76,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,夫婦不過是兩個不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.64,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法戰勝一心同體的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:32.31,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,轆轤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.02,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸都不一致
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.31,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,動作也不統一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.57,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話是贏不了我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.95,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:48.66,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,遭遇大危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.33,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.68,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:09.97,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.05,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.89,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:18.48,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.40,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,婆娑羅的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:21.94,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,抵消了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.40,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝 你……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.53,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一般的小丫頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:34.58,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的力量是不可能被碰巧彈開的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.33,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你……是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.92,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.34,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定擁有非比尋常的咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.80,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你是點心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.38,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:53.01,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們敢對小枝動手 俺可饒不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.81,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.14,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,陣之龜 鏡殲愧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.78,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們擋路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.24,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.66,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:15.53,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我是十二天將 青龍 水渡坂堪久郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.54,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,而這位守財奴是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:23.25,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,十二天將 玄武 雲林院憲剛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.38,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你別檀自做主啊 江湖郎中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:31.88,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,十二天將 太裳 嗎新 參上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.51,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 而且是三位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.77,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,十二天將的豪華陣容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.19,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,現門開鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.90,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,門好大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.41,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:53.74,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是現世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.33,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟比起充滿瘴氣的禍野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.08,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在現世戰鬥對我們更有利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.58,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,而且更有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.17,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 堪久郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.54,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不幹活的人就沒飯吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.34,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:11.88,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,能有三位十二天將大人助陣 實在感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.30,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:15.01,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拿五萬元來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.35,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,還要收錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.14,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,憲剛是個守財奴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.56,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是一般的守財奴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,通常價格是十萬元 我用學生優惠給你們打五折哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.65,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,用特別大優惠來幫助你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.69,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不需要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.15,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們的對決 給我閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.28,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:36.82,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,難得十二天將大人來助陣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:41.37,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 請你們後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:42.91,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,連紅緒大人都這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.46,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎？ 不向他們求助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:52.97,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,共鳴對我們沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.93,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,而且無論你們想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.18,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼事……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.55,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,欺負我家小枝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.68,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要親手祓除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:07.77,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,傷害小枝的人 由我們對付
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.65,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.99,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 相當不錯的咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.28,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 就跟你們玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.03,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們可不會再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.79,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,千千石 別大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.21,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,他們跟剛才不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:28.25,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 終究不是你我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.84,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然咒力和氣魄都有所提升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.22,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是僅此而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:40.01,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.81,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,搭檔不在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:46.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:53.48,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們……不能如你們那樣心靈相通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:57.57,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一點是很明確的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:03.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,即便被打倒了 轆轤也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.50,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,裂空魔彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.34,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,焰抵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:12.42,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,紅破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.26,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:23.68,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.83,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,說的煞有其事 結果只有這點程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.20,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼雙星……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.00,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.00,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,鎧包·白凜斗牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:54.92,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.46,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,玉兔 曉哭山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:04.43,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.08,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.42,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道 百道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.72,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,千千石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:51.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.46,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,終於出現了呢 暗無
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.71,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,中獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.34,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,切 堪久郎 我們追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:18.84,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.22,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,禍野門開鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:25.30,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,隧道的龍黑點拜託你了哦 新先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.52,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 剛才打開了龍黑點對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.14,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那個婆娑羅到底……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫暗無
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:39.23,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在追蹤那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.99,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,萬魔調伏 急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.09,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.85,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然十二天將很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.81,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是全是奇怪的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.64,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:22.32,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝 不可以做危險的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:25.28,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.45,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你們在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:29.66,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.08,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.55,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.01,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,千千石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:55.77,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.56,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.57,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,暗無 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:34.52,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道 百道 百道 百道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:40.06,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,雙星陰陽師造成的傷好像要了他的命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.45,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這是百道給你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.08,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道的咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:02.96,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,百道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.18,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的雙星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:22.10,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:26.86,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,完全彈開了婆娑羅的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.28,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那個力量是……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:36.91,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個力量到底是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.91,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝 為什麼你能使出那種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:42.88,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:45.92,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有想到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.21,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:48.38,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.59,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小枝 想去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:54.68,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的話 就是京都的方位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:55.97,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,京都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.35,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,京都裡有什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:00.98,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:05.15,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我有種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:47.47,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利福特先生說過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:52.27,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕人必須找出自己與眾不同的個性之種
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.61,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,並全力去培養它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:23:55.52,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:58.49,SUB-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 我也可以培養哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:24:00.00,T-title 方正,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1404,862)}秘密的繭良
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:18.68,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,100)}為了奪回逝去的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:25.56,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(500,100)}向天空釋放自己壓抑的感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:41.79,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(500,100)}我們是何時開始止步不前的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:47.58,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(500,100)}我們曾經發誓要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.50,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(500,100)}為了消除無法回應的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.34,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,100)}拚命趕赴約定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:58.34,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(500,100)}交錯在天空的兩顆星共同引導著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:03.81,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(500,100)}和你在一起能跨越任何艱難險阻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:09.31,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(500,100)}交錯的羈絆會成為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:12.36,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(500,100)}解放吧在黑暗中閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:15.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(500,100)}直指我們目標的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:21.95,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(500,100)}直到世界終結我們都要共同戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:27.33,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(500,100)}不管幾次我都會站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:31.21,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(500,100)}看向前方不要停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.38,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,100)}朝那片天空進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:18.68,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,100)}失くした光を取り戻すため
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:25.56,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(500,100)}空へ隠した感情を今解き放て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:41.79,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(500,100)}いつから立ち止まつてしまつたのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:47.58,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,100)}誰より強くなると誓つたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.50,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,100)}報えない過去消し去るように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.34,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,100)}追いかけ続ける約束の場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:58.34,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(500,100)}空に交わる二つの星が 共に導かれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:03.81,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,100)}君となら どんな道でも越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:09.31,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,100)}交わした絆が 力になつて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:12.36,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,100)}解き放て 闇を咲いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:15.11,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,100)}二人が目指す星へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:21.95,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(500,100)}この世界が終わるまでは 共に戦い続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:27.33,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(500,100)}何度も 何度も 立ち上かるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:31.21,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(500,100)}前を見て止まらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.38,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,100)}あの空へ
